### Conflicts
Reviewers, this pull request conflicts with the following ones:

* [#16539](https://drahtbot.github.io/bitcoin_core_issue_redirect/r/16539.html) (wallet: lower -txmaxfee default from 0.1 to
-0 on this, just because its almost only style changes. Anyway please squash and give a better commit message like `qa: Format extract_strings_qt.py and rpcauth.py with pep8` or something like that.

Thanks. However given this is just styling changes, and isn't mergable as is (multiple commits, no proper commit message etc), I'm going to close. Checkout the [good first issue](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22) list if you're interested in [contributing](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md).
